OL,7,FFiona Laskaris is calling for a change
OL,8,Fof law after fighting for years to get
OL,9,Fhelp for her vulnerable, autistic son,
OL,10,FChristopher, as ITV News Political
OL,11,FCorrespondent Romilly Weeks reports
OL,13,FSome readers may find the details in
OL,14,Fthis report distressing.
OL,16,FEight years on from the murder of 24-
OL,17,Fyear-old Christopher Laskaris, his
OL,18,Fmother Fiona is haunted by the many
OL,19,Fmissed opportunities there were to
OL,20,Fhelp her vulnerable, autistic son.
