OL,7,F"Losing a child is the worst thing
OL,8,Fthat can happen to anyone, but I think
OL,9,Fa preventable death is the very
OL,10,Fworst," she told ITV News. "It's the
OL,11,Ffact that someone could have done
OL,12,Fsomething."
OL,14,FChristopher struggled to live
OL,15,Findependently and was ultimately
OL,16,Fkilled in his own home by a convicted
OL,17,Fcriminal who took over his flat and
OL,18,Fexploited him.
