OL,7,FFiona is now calling for the law to be
OL,8,Fchanged so that the views of family
OL,9,Fmembers are taken into account when
OL,10,Fdeciding whether someone needs a
OL,11,Fmental capacity assessment.
OL,13,FHer cause has been backed by a cross-
OL,14,Fparty group of MPs, including the
OL,15,Fformer Health Secretary Jeremy Hunt,
OL,16,Fwho agree the current system is
OL,17,Ffailing autistic adults like
OL,18,FChristopher, as well as other adults
OL,19,Fwith learning disabilities and mental
OL,20,Fhealth illnesses.
