OL,8,Fwho moved into his flat, after police
OL,9,Fhad damaged the door following a
OL,10,Fwelfare check on Christopher.
OL,12,F"It was basically cuckooing, they were
OL,13,Fexploiting him," Fiona says, "and he
OL,14,Fcame back a few weeks later, gained
OL,15,Faccess to his flat and stabbed him
OL,16,Fthrough the heart.
OL,18,F"Christopher was left just dying on
OL,19,Fthe floor."
